| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0793 — Recovery Inhibition (embargo)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: cf18ee1e-cd1c-5612-9614-ed2d3c1ae0c8"
